The paper deals with social interactions and online social networks, which are typical topics in the sub-categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SOC (Computational Social Science). The paper also proposes a new research problem and an approximation algorithm, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
